The gene and the metabolite in the pathway

Source: R/pathwayinfo.R
pathwayinfo.Rd

The gene and the metabolite in the pathway

Usage

pathwayinfo(pathwayid)

Arguments

pathwayid

the pathway id, hsa or name

Value

the genes and metabolites KEGG ID corresponding to pathway

Examples

result <- pathwayinfo("hsa00630")
result
